Just Tall is not another Big and Tall store. Just Tall is run by a tall, lean guy, for tall, lean guys. We are an exclusive but simple men's clothing brand targeting tall, lean to athletic men of all age groups between 6'2 and 7'2. Our clothing embodies two basic characteristics: longer, not wider - the simple formula to providing a reliable fit for the vertically gifted, not the horizontally gifted. We aim to launch with casual wear (crew neck t-shirts, polo t-shirts, and jeans) and active wear (t-shirts and gym pants) Our differentiators include a premium range for more up-market clientele, and a sizing plugin built into the product page to enhance the customer experience and reduce returns. If we were to describe our brand with one word, it would be simple: Simple in the product selection, simple design styles, simple ordering and shipping processes, simple product pages, simple social media communications and visual aesthetic, and a simple conversational style with customers without being too funny or too serious.
